{
  "texts": [
    "Nonetheless, when eye video data were not recorded, sound data were likewise not recorded, hence some data were missing in this regard.",
    "For Annotation Level 3, only 61 out of 7763 annotations were missing, accounting for 0.78% of total annotations.",
    "For Annotation Level 4, 19 annotations were missing, representing 0.24% of the total.",
    "Finally, in the case of Annotation Level 5, there were 857 missing annotations, accounting for 11.04% of the total annotations.",
    "During the data collection process, some video data was missing."
  ]
}